title: THE ROAST OF THE 2008 FLORIDA GATORS
description:
Our unstoppable train of Dawg-respecting is blasting through your tiny town to bring you the good news: the 2008 Florida football team was not very good!

Boats These Days: Are they too big now?

"Fellas, is it gay to be buried in the earth after death?" Worry no more!

Midway through this episode, Spencer begins insisting that Jason Statham, the actor, has "range"; best of luck hanging on until the end.
